reviews.headline: So glad I tried this BOBBI BROWN eyeshadow stick
reviews.comments: I was preparing for a destination wedding and thought how easily my eye shadow pallets could be damaged during flights, Uber etc. I read reviews and decided to try the BOBBI BROWN cream eyeshadow stick. I as so glad as I Love It. It is so easy to apply, doesn't crease and lasts all day. I will be purchasing more colors.

A swipe of this, mascara, undereye concealer & you can head out the door!

reviews.headline: kinda disappointed.
reviews.comments:
The only thing I liked about this was the texture, it was very creamy/soft and just glided right on. 

Problem #1 is that I ordered Moonstone based on the color "swipe" (2nd picture in the group) and it's much more like the tiny swatch that they show on the arms - much more golden than pink. So I'm not sure if the first few photos are accurate. That's a real bummer because I purposefully picked that color (not the gold one). I would recommend seeing the colors in person before you buy. 

Problem #2 is when I attempted to wash it off - glitter was ALL OVER MY FACE. I use a foamy makeup remover face wash to remove makeup first, then my actual face wash 2nd. I still had glitter on my cheeks and near my eyes so I tried using my 'strong' makeup remover and still didn't get it off, so I had to wash my face again. 

it's just not worth in my opinion, when I have other brands that glide on, stay well through the day, and remove easily.  I purchased because it was on sale and I was trying to find a replacement for another brand w/ that specific color.

reviews.headline: LOVE THIS EYESHADOW
reviews.comments: Thanks to Jacko at Ulta Canton, I now have the perfect eyeshadow! I've tried so many, but Bobbi Brown Long-Wear Waterproof Cream Stick is the one for me. It's very natural looking on my old eyes and looks the same all day long. Thank you, Jacko!

reviews.headline: Love it!!!
reviews.comments: I absolutely adore the Bobbi Brown waterproof and sweat-resistant eyebrow pencil that was generously gifted to me by Bobbi Brown! Its unique, flat edge design allows me to effortlessly create both soft, natural looks and bold, striking shapes with precision. With each application, my brows appear beautifully styled and incredibly lifelike. The range of natural shades is perfect for seamlessly harmonizing with my hair color, enhancing my overall look. I truly appreciate how this pencil keeps my eyebrows looking impeccably polished and perfectly defined throughout the entire day, no matter the conditions!

faceoff_positive.comments: I am 50y/o and still cannot apply eyeshadow without looking like I've joined the circus! This eyeshadow is amazing! It makes application very easy for me and the colors I chose are rich and velvety. There is never any crumbled ressidue that regular powder shadows always seem to settle in crease under my eyes and colors stayed on all day. I chose vanilla and stone for daytime look on my dark brown eyes and medium fair complexion. I am so happy with the results/quality/ease that I'm now wanting a third color.. I wish THIS line offered eyeshadow samples, since the price for one is a little more pricey than what I used to pay, that way, we can see how colors look. GREAT IDEA /marketing TO WHOMEVER is reviewing my comments... Bobbi Brown offers color swatches for their foundation, which I love too, but needs to consider samples for eyeshadows... I recommend eye makeup remover for taking off, since this creamy shadow def hugs onto your lids...
faceoff_positive.headline: BOBBI BROWN CREAM EYESHADOW STICK

faceoff_negative.comments: This review pertains only to Pink Sparkle, which I thought had a terrible texture. It looked grainy and felt the same. I was hoping to use it as a highlight color, but because of the thick grainy texture it looked so unflattering. I couldn't create the sheer wash that I was hoping for. Very disappointing.
faceoff_negative.headline: No to Pink Sparkle
